•Total Productive Management (TPM) Expert having led the implementation at site and corporate level in Asia, Africa and Europe. Large experience with JIPM Audits been part of several successful TPM Awards assessments at the Excellence, Consistence and Special Award levels;
•TPM assessor and trainer having delivered more than 15 training sessions: TPM coaches course, Autonomous Management, Planned Maintenance, Quality Maintenance and Focused Improvement. Practical Lean Six Sigma knowledge having led Value Stream Design activities in Ukraine;
