•Good experience implementing and coordinating Integrated Management Systems including ISO 9000:2001, ISO 14001:2004 and OSHAS 18001;
•Pragmatic, organized and highly self-motivated to drive change and continuous Improvement. Creative, Flexible, sensible to organization differences to drive smoothly all required changes which are required by the continuous improvement process being implemented;
•Highly capable to build strong relationships seeking constantly opportunities to communicate aiming to contribute and learn in win/win relationships;
•Focused to develop colleagues and subordinates through constant feedback, coaching and mentoring;
•Results oriented having led and supported problem solving working groups as line manager and as continuous improvement manager achieving important results.

